<noinclude>This is the "EntityMap" template.

It is created by Shuchang. Contact me if you find any bug or have any improvement. 

It should be called in the following format: (it can be written in single line.)

<pre>
{{EntityMap
|latitude={{{latitude}}}
|longitude={{{longitude}}}
|zoom=17  // Optional. Set this parameter ONLY when you want a different zoom level. Default value is 17  
|minzoom=17 // Optional. This should be the same as parameter 'zoom'. Default value is 17
|maxzoom=17 // Optional. This should be the same as parameter 'zoom'. Default value is 17
|service=googlemaps // Optional. Default value is Google Maps.
}}</pre>

In most of entity pages, it should be called simply as
<pre>
{{EntityMap|latitude={{{latitude}}}|longitude={{{longitude}}}}}
</pre>
or
<pre>
{{EntityMap
|latitude={{{latitude}}}
|longitude={{{longitude}}}
|zoom=12  
|minzoom=12 
|maxzoom=12 
}}
</pre>
</noinclude>
<includeonly>{{#display_map: {{#if: {{{latitude|}}} | {{{latitude|}}} | 40.758153}}, {{#if: {{{longitude|}}} | {{{longitude|}}} | -73.985355}}  
|zoom={{#if: {{{zoom|}}} | {{{zoom|}}} | 17}}  

|service={{#if: {{{service|}}} | {{{service|}}} | googlemaps}} 
}}</includeonly>
